---
title: White Bean Chicken Chili with Spiced Tortilla Chips
description: This hearty chili, packed with filling cannellini beans, will keep the winter chills at bay! Crush the spiced tortilla chips over top for a delightful crunch, or use them to scoop up every last bite!
